{"tid":700430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣技工墮地 開腦兩次性命垂危","createTime":"2018-06-13T10:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T14:56:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8c588e88b6262280b3bd842107299172afbdfe","tid":700430,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180613/20419382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F20419382&d=vW5%2B4s5mdenZ%2FfTCoObt%2BtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d8e6f432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F20419382&h=48145297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180613/20419382</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月13日 <br />\n<br />\n冷氣技工墮地<br />\n開腦兩次性命垂危<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】荃新天地前晚發生嚴重的工業意外，一名47歲姓高的冷氣技工從約4米高的人字梯墮下，重傷昏迷，送入瑪嘉烈醫院救治後留醫深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，受傷工人47歲，未婚，與90歲的母親同住葵涌區，二人一直相依為命，他亦是家中的重要經濟支柱。據其家人透露，高男為人孝順，擔起照顧年老母親的責任，對她呵護備至，早前更在母親節陪她食飯過節。家人又引述醫生透露，前日院方已替高男進行腦部手術，惟他腦壓仍然偏高，遂昨日下午再替他進行腦部手術，現時他的情況暫時樂觀，未有生命危險，但仍需作詳細檢查及觀察。<br />\n<br />\n工業傷亡權益會得悉事件後，已派出社工及同事到醫院了解，並預備向傷者家屬提供一切可行協助。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【動畫】3Cap帽男擸棒球棍　掃九龍城酒吧"},{"pid":"9ec2609af63375df67b018e440ea497e19196415","tid":700430,"uid":11809,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"大步檻過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caee85194886f737519d8205ad7477854b95b19e","tid":700430,"uid":70786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"返工=危險"},{"pid":"50375feebc5c4dd6ba59780e38d030f8c9d0dfbf","tid":700430,"uid":34184,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"昨晚六合彩開獎結果???"},{"pid":"23ec708119abb786af938903bc85706ac3760d85","tid":700430,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"47歲，未婚<br />\n<br />\n射係佢就寧願放棄治療"},{"pid":"0e83afa7247e18284675f1890668dedcec9655d5","tid":700430,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ec708119abb786af938903bc85706ac3760d85","tid":700430,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"47歲，未婚<br />\n<br />\n射係佢就寧願放棄治療"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ee9428e206a6f008bbf8f4852571060ba94f99","tid":700430,"uid":25899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ec708119abb786af938903bc85706ac3760d85","tid":700430,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"47歲，未婚<br />\n<br />\n射係佢就寧願放棄治療"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"55894c4e7b29354b7168f20cc45c8f9b5088a3af","tid":700430,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"caee85194886f737519d8205ad7477854b95b19e","tid":700430,"uid":70786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"返工=危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"d390ff3f6b69c0f456ddbe74ef69f17cd355227b","tid":700430,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ec708119abb786af938903bc85706ac3760d85","tid":700430,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"47歲，未婚<br />\n<br />\n射係佢就寧願放棄治療"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"47歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img